node.text:
The TRUTH about automated income.

Maybe you heard people talk about passive income…

I personally believe that passive income is a myth. Because nothing is truly passive. 

Even if you invest in stocks or something, you still need to check in on it once in a while.

So, instead of aiming for passive income, go for automated income.

It means you put in some work upfront.

And once it gains momentum, you keep making money without you being there.

Then you just need to do maintenance work once in a while.

Automated income is how nearly all wealthy people created their wealth. 

It’s almost impossible to create real wealth if you trade your time for money…

That’s why automated income is so important.

Looking for a beginner-friendly skill or side hustle that will help you automate your income?

Selling products on Amazon FBA is your best pick.

follow 👉 @bjkuniversity 
follow 👉 @bjkuniversity
follow 👉 @bjkuniversity

And they’ll show you how it’s done.

Here's how a business should run:

You don't have to work in it all the time
Your team loves to work WITH you, not just for you
You can spend most of your time on things you love

This is how I run my Amazon FBA and FBA education businesses. I don't have employees, I have partners who win if the company grows. No matter if it's marketing, sales or customers, we're all in the same boat and share the same vision: To make a dent in the universe by impacting the lives of 1 million people at a time. By now, even my successful students wanna join in and create content for BJK-University!

Follow 👉 @bjkuniversity 
Follow 👉 @bjkuniversity
Follow 👉 @bjkuniversity

And see for yourself what impact you can have with a business like Amazon FBA!

node.text:
Disclaimer: Never start a business you don’t understand! Get educated first, to minimize your risks of losing money.

Selling on Amazon is a great business for anyone who never ran a business before.

That’s because, compared to most other businesses, your starting capital is low.

(I recommend about $5-6k to start.)

The most important thing you need is a winning product.

And there are lots of strategies to find good products....

For example, the method I teach allows you to make a profit of 25% on every product you sell. 

Most sellers break even after 1-2 months this way…

And with just $6k of initial investments, they make over $70k in a year.

But all of this only is possible if you know what you are doing!

So, take time to learn the ins and outs of Amazon first.

follow 👉 @bjkuniversity 
follow 👉 @bjkuniversity
follow 👉 @bjkuniversity

...and they’ll show you how it’s done.

node.text:
Are you waiting for things to be perfect?

Here’s something I noticed:

Most people aren’t really living.

They have dreams and goals but they don’t allow themselves to go after them.

Do you know why? Because they are waiting for the perfect time.

They wait for everything to fall perfectly into place…

And then, they tell themselves, then they would get started…

Can you relate?

If you do read this next sentence with your full attention:

The timing will NEVER be perfect.

Things will NEVER fall into place.

That’s why perfection equals paralysis.

Perfection simply doesn’t exist. 

Focus on progress instead and live your life NOW!

------------------------------------------------------
On the journey to freedom? Hit that follow button! ⬇️👍

🔷 @basharjkatou
🔷 @basharjkatou
🔷 @basharjkatou
------------------------------------------------------

node.text:
I’m NOT saying burn yourself out and hustle every minute…

But what I am saying is that you can always find the time to work on your goals.

For example:

Instead of watching silly YouTube videos…

Instead of binging netflix…

Instead of overthinking…

You can use the time to learn something new or work on a goal you had for years.

It’s not just about how much time you have…

It’s how you use the time you have.

My recommendation for you:

Calculate for yourself how much time you have each week.

I’m sure you’ll be surprised.

And when you are ready to invest your time to start a business or side hustle…

follow 👉 @bjkuniversity

Tell me why 97% of people :

are unsuccessful
are unfulfilled
have no control over their time
Barely can afford to live
hate their jobs and lives

It's not even their fault.

We live in a world where your network is your net worth and kids learn not to talk to strangers, and "networking" during class makes you fail.

This makes no sense to me.

You spend years learning irrelevant knowledge, that 5 five second Google search could tell you…

But not how to make it in life?

But that's what you get for following the system: Social anxiety, stress and being unhappy.

Of course not everyone feels like this. 

The system is not made for entrepreneurs, so we won't be happy like that and gotta take life into our own hands and solve the problem together.

Who else will teach people like us to be happy if we don't learn from each other?

That's why, if you wanna be an entrepreneur, don't be a lone wolf.

Get help and...

follow 👉 @bjkuniversity
